{"tid":1468831,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"乖姐姐呵返 唔好嘈交","createTime":"2019-08-13T21:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T22:43:16.000Z","uid":306266,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cfa577b4ebc36db673d10a77d22d730f16d71d06","tid":1468831,"uid":306266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T21:36:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">家和萬事興 家衰口不停</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家一家人，床頭嗌交床尾和，以後繼續齊齊整整出嚟夢遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />始終人多，意見自然多，無可避免有分歧，唯有盡量諗下次點做好啲。團結未必會贏，成盤散沙咁就一定輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />近排大家都辛苦好攰，心情唔好，姐姐錫返。呢個moment要keep住道火，都要記得適當release 負能量，唔介意既可以揾我傾，我樂意做出氣袋<br />\n<br />\n我仲期待緊有一日可以真正開開心心一齊玩鐳射筆，好想再見到你地真摯既笑容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我好愛你地每一個香港人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屋企日日嘈到家無寧日，最近想搬。窮撚我想問有冇人屋企有空房可以<span style=\"color: red;\">長期</span>租比我，梳化都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我淨係想要個位瞓覺沖涼屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者<span style=\"color: red;\">長期</span>合租，不過我筆直唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申:乾淨有手尾。好靜，唔中意太嘈，其他可以就你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"0aeb8cd09be8367083256a69bbd69d68e7312741","tid":1468831,"uid":61084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:43:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 姐姐你好<br />\n介唔介意同Dee dee一齊住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}